{{Remarks_Section
|Remarks=In the following example, the instantiated array object is the same as the return value of this method.

 var arr = [1, 2, 3, 4];
 var s = arr.valueOf();
 
 if (arr === s)
 document.write("same");
 else
 document.write("different");
 
 // Output:
 // same
